{"tid":1566142,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"堅係良心鋪頭，學生真係唔收錢（真免費已FC），話我打手都係咁話","createTime":"2019-09-13T12:31:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T02:13:00.000Z","uid":315870,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"278d1933c1ead56cbebb104e2b396031c2448f80","tid":1566142,"uid":315870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:31:32.000Z","msg":"今日去完紅磡嗰間「龍門冰室」,入去之前靜靜雞問左個店員學生係唔係免費,佢話「系\u0000!」<br />\n<br />\n  原本都以為要買其他嘢食先可以用到個優惠,落單嘅時候問起個店員,原來學生真係完全唔使畀錢!!!落完單之後個店員會對你好似普通客,唔會特別話你係免費。走嘅時候畀張單店員就得,真係一毫子都唔使俾。<br />\n<br />\n 呢啲良心鋪頭去邊度搵到?佢啲租金好平?唔係,而係個老闆真心想幫學生,自己貼錢都要落去都要畀呢個優惠。入到去鋪頭又唔使特別講話自己係免費,熱心嘅店員會當你係普通客對待。<br />\n<br />\n  佢間餐廳入邊嘅野食真係好撚正,大大碗面,煎雙蛋,脆博博嘅餐肉,仲有大大杯嘢飲。老世真係蝕住嚟做。<br />\n<br />\n  發夢冇錢嘅兄弟即管入去試下,入到去衹要出示學生證就可以。有錢嘅就真係咪撚用呢個優惠,以後食多啲!!!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n  冇乜嘢可以畀返個老世,淨係希望呢篇野可以令多啲人識良心鋪頭。<br />\n  唔掂嘅兄弟唔好怕醜，食飽飽再發夢。<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/LungMunCafe/posts/2616746305056837\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FLungMunCafe%2Fposts%2F2616746305056837&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88qVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=3e78018b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/LungMunCafe/posts/2616746305056837</a><br />\n<br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"618aae80ac925b175844cda56f3959919ad209d0","tid":1566142,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:32:01.000Z","msg":"[國際戰線] 香港人唔可以當其他國家係Condom!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1565130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1565130</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/thrHTWT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FthrHTWT.jpg&h=21d791c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2bc88f1e057695f1a5cc3beeb4bb6647d7647f4","tid":1566142,"uid":315870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:32:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"555e7a21ce6068c9d84996c1d404fbfb651d293a","tid":1566142,"uid":315870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:32:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f17cd1bd7e2bfb9bef6728cb7eee52d10d6133b8","tid":1566142,"uid":315870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:32:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c7f9fc1b0d701b2f9804ef18c521307765b3d123","tid":1566142,"uid":315870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:33:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6aec15f60dfc6b3b9939bd5d78268bb8c6307a34","tid":1566142,"uid":21340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:33:19.000Z","msg":"感謝老闆，好人一生平安"},{"pid":"f858f3861eff269935c56377473a17472e143192","tid":1566142,"uid":260036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:33:25.000Z","msg":"下次放飯去幫襯下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好人一生平安"},{"pid":"d5b14b952056b89ecbceee2c0dc8a9ebbfebcb2e","tid":1566142,"uid":315870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6aec15f60dfc6b3b9939bd5d78268bb8c6307a34","tid":1566142,"uid":21340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:33:19.000Z","msg":"感謝老闆，好人一生平安"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:33:34.000Z","msg":"幫手推一推!!!"},{"pid":"98753aa78247957600aae252b3651027bcf1d31e","tid":1566142,"uid":315870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f858f3861eff269935c56377473a17472e143192","tid":1566142,"uid":260036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:33:25.000Z","msg":"下次放飯去幫襯下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好人一生平安"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:34:03.